{"about_the_game":"The object of the game is to escape the castle with as much wealth as possible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo escape you will need to collect five keys and solve the final puzzle.<br />\r\nThere is a key in each of the five towers, and the entrances to some of these towers are locked or hidden.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game is full of puzzles; some need to be solved to gain access to rooms and navigate the castle. Others need to be solved to collect the valuables and increase your wealth.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are gold coins, goblets, candlesticks, plates and jewels to collect throughout the castle. Some are in plain sight and easy to collect, some have to be earned by solving a puzzle and some are hidden so be observant.<br />\r\nThere are collectable's that are needed to gain access to valuables or other rooms.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBe careful as you explore this castle there are a few dangers that can injure you.<br />\r\nCollect the food to replenish your health if you do get injured.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is a dungeon in the castle but you will need to find and solve a puzzle to get the key for the gate. There is a 'torture chamber' if you can figure out how to gain access, two mazes that you need to find you way through and many more rooms.<br />\r\nThere are many different types of puzzle to solve, some interconnected, some standalone, with different types of clues and hints throughout the game.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wealthy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1629220/edadc58fc87f42a7c77dfdc346ab335bd9e019e3.jpg"},{"name":"Speedy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1629220/d305c4b4fcb5cbc5af770ba8fb7fcf6b34644428.jpg"},{"name":"Great Puzzler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1629220/c8bc83c3c497dafc9eec4ad34b91f4e1c0382ec7.jpg"},{"name":"Dragon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity